text: The Sweden women's national under-18 and under-19 basketball team is the national women's basketball team that represents Sweden in international under-18 and under-19 (under age 19 and under age 18) tournaments. The team is controlled by the Svenska Basketbollförbundet. ==See also== *Sweden women's national basketball team *Sweden women's national under-17 basketball team ==References== ==External links== *Official website *FIBA profile B Category:Women's national under-19 basketball teams
